  <exercise>
    <introduction>
        <p>
           Consider the weighted voting system <m>[38 | 22, 20, 17, 9, 5]</m> 
        </p>
    </introduction>
    <task>
      <statement>
        <p>
          In the system, consider the winning coalition <m>\{P_2, P_3, P_4, P_5\}</m>.  
          Which voters are critical voters in this coalition?
        </p>
      </statement>
      <answer>
        <p><m>P_2</m> and <m>P_3</m> are critical voters (the 20 and the 17).</p>
      </answer>
    </task>
  </exercise>

